<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<h2 id="head-37ad2cc642be45bcbedec21c5b37640b05d28be6">The Long Bow of Bard (x5) (+17,+19)</h2>
<em>The great yew bow of grim-faced Bard, who shot the mightiest arrow that songs record.</em> <em><strong>It is from a group of items rumoured to be the bane of dragons.</strong></em> <p>
It increases your dexterity and luck by 2. It provides immunity to paralysis. It allows you to sense the presence of dragons. It fires missiles with extra might. 
</p>
